name: ONE Season 1 (Episodes 1-9)
description: ONE: Season One[1] is the first season of ONE. A teaser was released on January 12, 2020 and its first episode, "Freefall", was released on June 11, 2020. The season would conclude on July 19, 2021, with the episode "Scatterbrain". On October 11, 2022, a 1 hour 22 minute compilation of all 9 episodes from the season was released on Cheesy Hfj's channel.
